{"tid":600950,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲想過自殺?","createTime":"2018-03-21T20:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T19:02:43.000Z","uid":146222,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"361ac824ce42ffda1f8180b9f6d30261a04f2cbe","tid":600950,"uid":146222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T20:49:03.000Z","msg":"我係一個做咩都半途而廢嘅廢人<br />\n每份工都唔會做得耐<br />\n又冇幾個朋友係可以交心<br />\n有乜事都只係可以放喺個心裏面<br />\n<br />\n我屋企又有問題<br />\n父母冷戰咗好耐<br />\n每日都驚佢地會開片<br />\n離婚又離唔成<br />\n<br />\n有時我只係想有人大力咁擁抱我<br />\n比我盡情痛哭<br />\n<br />\n有時忍唔住會喺被窩到喊<br />\n見到自己只感覺到絕望<br />\n<br />\n人地成日話我仲慘過你啦，我咪咁生活落去<br />\n我認我抗逆能力低<br />\n心入面有把聲叫我自殺<br />\n我知要撐住<br />\n但我冇人地咁堅強<br />\n我唔知可以捱得幾耐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47f3b018742e10a95e2c8edd40c94b201715cdc","tid":600950,"uid":170616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T20:51:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得手巴會入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e70276ede8783c6ba0c8fe0b34447fd8752f098","tid":600950,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47f3b018742e10a95e2c8edd40c94b201715cdc","tid":600950,"uid":170616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T20:51:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得手巴會入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T20:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你贏"},{"pid":"f59eebd6caedbefc1ff2cabaa350e2630292bf4f","tid":600950,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"361ac824ce42ffda1f8180b9f6d30261a04f2cbe","tid":600950,"uid":146222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T20